{
  "id": "61cc9ed7047334001d9e8e26",
  "title": "ダブル(ゲームデザイン)",
  "created": 1640799963,
  "updated": 1640859062,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61cc9ed7047334001d9e8e26",
      "text": "ダブル(ゲームデザイン)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640799963,
      "updated": 1640799969
    },
    {
      "id": "61cc9eebaff09e00008f3b47",
      "text": "ゲームを効率よく終わらせるメカニズム",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640799983,
      "updated": 1640800102
    },
    {
      "id": "61cc9f2baff09e00008f3b4a",
      "text": " https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/バックギャモン",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640800043,
      "updated": 1640800044
    },
    {
      "id": "61cc9f24aff09e00008f3b48",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640800036,
      "updated": 1640800036
    },
    {
      "id": "61cc9f24aff09e00008f3b49",
      "text": "勝てば勝ち点1が得られるゲームにおいて劣勢側はどんなに自分の勝つ確率pが小さくてもゲームを継続することによる勝ち点期待値pが投了時の勝ち点期待値0を上回るので投了しない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640800036,
      "updated": 1640800225
    },
    {
      "id": "61cc9fefaff09e00008f3b4b",
      "text": "ここでプレイヤーに「勝ち点を倍にする提案」ができるようにする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640800239,
      "updated": 1640800275
    },
    {
      "id": "61cca094aff09e00008f3b4c",
      "text": "この提案を",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640800404,
      "updated": 1640800792
    },
    {
      "id": "61cca217aff09e000007cdc3",
      "text": "\t受けると",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640800792,
      "updated": 1640800792
    },
    {
      "id": "61cca205aff09e000007cdc1",
      "text": " \t相手の得る点数の期待値 [$ 2(1-p)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640800774,
      "updated": 1640800859
    },
    {
      "id": "61cca208aff09e000007cdc2",
      "text": " \t自分の得る点数の期待値 [$ 2p]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640800776,
      "updated": 1640800863
    },
    {
      "id": "61cca111aff09e00008f3b4e",
      "text": "\t受けないと",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640800530,
      "updated": 1640800796
    },
    {
      "id": "61cca21baff09e000007cdc4",
      "text": "\t\t投了扱いなので",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640800796,
      "updated": 1640800806
    },
    {
      "id": "61cca226aff09e000007cdc5",
      "text": "\t\t\t相手の得る点数の期待値1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640800806,
      "updated": 1640800806
    },
    {
      "id": "61cc9eeaaff09e00008f3b46",
      "text": "\t \t自分の得る点数の期待値 0",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640799983,
      "updated": 1640800814
    },
    {
      "id": "61cca229aff09e000007cdc6",
      "text": "\t[$ 2p - 2(1-p) =  2(2p-1) > -1 = 0 - 1 ] が [$ p < 1/4] のときなりたつので受けた方が得",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640800810,
      "updated": 1640801018
    },
    {
      "id": "61cca241aff09e000007cdc7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640800834,
      "updated": 1640800834
    },
